locality: Yemen, gov. Hadramout, in the town Fuwwah (near the Eastern Coastal Branch of AREA).

Yemen: Gov. Al-Mahra. sand dune region 3 km W of Haswayn. Dunes 1-1.5 m tall, formed by Odyssea shrubs, additionally a vegetation of geophytes and theropyhtes (few days after heavy rains). Alt.: 10-20 m. 17.11.2000, Leg.: P. Hein, N. Kilian & C. Naumann PH 8263.
Yemen: Lahj. 30 km NWN of Aden. Alt.: 70 m. 3.3.1996, Leg.: P. Hein & E. von Raab-Straube PH 3.
Yemen: Gov. Abyan. Abyan plain, 15 km WSW of Shaqra. Alt.: 1-5 m. 26.3.1997, Leg.: P. Hein, A. N. Al Gifri, N. Kilian & M. Smalla PH 3650.
